               <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">In this section parent CC refers to the CF1R Certificate of Compliance.  
This section is applicable if at least one drain water heat recovery system in Section B has B11_DWHR_Type == DWHR Or  at least one drain water heat recovery system in Section B2 has Hpi09_.DWHR_Type == DWHR.   Require one row of data for each drain water heat recovery system with B11_DWHR_Type == DWHR Or Hpi09_.DWHR_Type == DWHR.</xs:documentation>
               
               
               <xs:documentation source="MinOccurs">If this section doesn't apply, display only the section FieldText and the statement 'This section does not apply to this project.'</xs:documentation>
               
            
