                        <xs:documentation source="AdditionalRequirements">The DWHR unit(s) shall be installed within 1 degree of the rated slope.  Sloped DWHR shall have a minimum lengthwise slope of 1 degree.  The lateral level tolerance shall be within plus or minus 1 degree.</xs:documentation>
                        
                     
