               <xs:documentation source="FieldText">Verified Central Parallel Piping Requirements (PP-H) (RA3.6.4)</xs:documentation>
               
               
               <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">This section is required if at least one water heating system has A09_ResidentialDHWDwellingUnitDistributionType   == StandardDistributionCentralParallelPipingHERS Or at least one water heating system has Section A2 Hpd07_ResidentialDHWDwellingUnitDistributionType == StandardDistributionCentralParallelPipingHERS</xs:documentation>
               
               
